WEBVTT

00:01.268 --> 00:04.003
<i>Previously on</i> Greenleaf...

00:04.003 --> 00:06.739
- I had a really nice time tonight.
- Yeah, me, too.

00:06.741 --> 00:08.507
<i>He pecked me on the cheek.</i>

00:08.509 --> 00:09.675
I don't know if there's
something wrong with me

00:09.677 --> 00:12.011
or if I just attract
a certain type.

00:12.013 --> 00:14.279
- I don't think he's gay.
- I don't know what he is.

00:14.281 --> 00:17.216
Lionel, you just gonna
swoop in here and save me,

00:17.218 --> 00:19.251
prove to me that I should've
run off with you

00:19.253 --> 00:20.452
when I had a chance?

00:20.454 --> 00:22.488
My wife Kerissa
and I have taken up

00:22.490 --> 00:26.025
the Lord's challenge to found
the Real Church of Memphis,

00:26.027 --> 00:29.228
a ministry dedicated to serving
the homeless and hopeless.

00:29.230 --> 00:30.662
I used to be married.

00:30.664 --> 00:33.465
We were on our way to a matinee
one Sunday afternoon,

00:33.467 --> 00:35.801
and we got Tboned
in an intersection.

00:35.803 --> 00:38.070
I asked a pastor
after the funeral

00:38.072 --> 00:39.738
if he could help me understand.

00:39.740 --> 00:42.307
He said it's best
we don't question God.

00:42.309 --> 00:44.576
So I haven't been back
to church since.

00:44.578 --> 00:46.645
- We cover the debt.
- You give us Triumph II.

00:46.647 --> 00:48.814
That way the money gets replaced
and you don't go to jail.

00:48.816 --> 00:51.650
Just give me two weeks. I've owed you
50 before, and I've come up with it.

00:51.652 --> 00:54.353
So Basie lost the church's
money, not his own.

00:54.355 --> 00:56.722
- That's right.
- And you two paid it back?

00:56.724 --> 00:58.724
Yes. We got the land
and the house,

00:58.726 --> 01:01.093
- but we should've gotten Triumph.
- Can you prove it?

01:03.000 --> 01:09.074
